= = 1992 Men 's Basketball Team ( Barcelona ) - The Dream Team = = In 1989 , FIBA , international basketball 's governing body , allowed professional NBA players to participate in the Olympics for the first time .
Before the 1992 Summer Olympics , only European and South American professionals were allowed to play in the Olympics .
1992 roster .
